\title{Shocked POststarbust Galaxy Survey I: Candidate Poststarbust Galaxies with Emission Line Ratios Consistent with Shocks}
\author{Katherine Alatalo,$^{1,2}$\altaffilmark{$\dagger$} Sabrina~L. Cales,$^{3,4}$ Jeffrey~A. Rich,$^{1,2}$ Philip~N. Appleton,$^{2,5}$ Lisa J. Kewley,$^{6}$ Mark Lacy,$^{7}$ Lauranne Lanz,$^{2}$ Anne~M. Medling,$^{6}$ \& Kristina Nyland$^{7}$
